<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">خ ض ب:</span> <span class="c2">(الْخِضَابُ)</span> مَا يُخْتَضَبُ بِهِ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(خَضَبَهُ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ ضَرَبَ وَ <span class="c2">(اخْتَضَبَ)</span> بِالْحِنَّاءِ وَنَحْوِهِ، وَكَفٌّ <span class="c2">(خَضِيبٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْمِخْضَبُ)</span> الْمِرْكَنُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>